prompt:
"Create a series of premium, professional landscape 16:9 hero section images for the website of a company called Hekayah Advertising Gifts & Supplies, located in Sharjah, UAE. The images should immediately communicate the brand’s business idea: a one-stop advertising and promotional solutions provider with 14+ years of experience.

Each image should look modern, clean, and corporate, with a premium advertising aesthetic. Include visual themes such as:

Corporate Branding: Branded stationery, business cards, brochures, and calendars beautifully arranged.

Signage & Large Format Printing: A professional office/storefront with glowing signage, wall branding, vehicle wraps, and banners.

Exhibition & Events: Backdrops, roll-up banners, and display stands in a sleek exhibition booth setup.

Corporate Gifts & Lifestyle: High-end promotional products like pens, notebooks, mugs, tote bags, trophies, and tech gadgets displayed elegantly.

Flags & Textiles: Vibrant flags, fabric items, and textile-based branding in use at an event.

Style: Modern, premium, high-quality marketing visuals with bright lighting, clean white or branded corporate backgrounds, sharp focus, and a professional business look. No text in the images. The goal is that visitors instantly understand this is a trusted advertising and branding solutions company."

magic_prompt_output: A sleek product shot advertisement showcasing Hekayah Advertising Gifts & Supplies, presenting a curated arrangement of branded corporate items against a clean, minimalist white background. The composition features premium stationery – embossed business cards, a leather-bound notebook, and a modern calendar – alongside a selection of promotional products like elegant pens, a branded tote bag, and a polished trophy, all meticulously arranged to convey quality and sophistication. Soft, diffused lighting highlights the textures and details of each item, creating a sharp, professional aesthetic with a focus on impeccable branding and design, embodying Hekayah's 14+ years of experience providing advertising and promotional solutions. The overall mood is corporate, trustworthy, and premium, instantly communicating Hekayah as a reliable partner for all advertising and branding needs, reflecting the tagline "Your Brand. Our Expertise."
